cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.CE 

The paper discusses the coordination of electric vehicle charging, which involves game theory and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics). The paper also uses concepts from machine learning (cs.LG), control systems (cs.SY), mathematical optimization (cs.MA), and computer engineering (cs.CE) to analyze the efficiency of the proposed algorithms.
